					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11638377#post-4243720</guid>
				<title>SCP-4152</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11638377/scp-4152#post-4243720</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2019 18:18:47 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>devonmartin</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1985558</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is my second scip, and no matter how many more I write, this one will always be the hardest.</p> <p>Special thanks to the artist for granting permission to use their painting for this article (taken from Instagram @paint.goon).</p> <p>Thanks to Crashington for the critique.</p> <p>Happy Mother's Day!</p> <hr /> <p>If this article brings back memories of your own, just know <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/raisedbynarcissists/">you're not alone</a>.</p> <hr /> <p>This SCP is based on &quot;BASEMENT LOVE,&quot; a work by the immensely talented Gio Martin. Taken from <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/BwdTrnJF95_/">https://www.instagram.com/p/BwdTrnJF95_/</a></p> 
				 	]]>
